                    <span>I really like this book-it really shows what an absolutely beautiful lady she was-she certainly was very sensual and sexy.She knew how to project herself without going overboard-<BR>the lady had class and it really showed.There aren't any actresses like Audrey anymore-I really miss her.<P>I highly recommend getting this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Delivery doesn't match topic</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
